title: NFL Inside Report - Urban Meyer’s failed NFL journey, where do the Jags turn now?
itunes:title: NFL Inside Report - Urban Meyer’s failed NFL journey, where do the Jags turn now?
description:
In the 43rd episode of the NFL Inside Report podcast, Rhett Lewis is joined by insider Judy Battista for perspective on Urban Meyer's mistakes that led to his firing in Jacksonville after coaching just 13 games. Then Rhett and Judy discuss who the Jacksonville Jaguars should consider as their next head coach.
